 all sessions complete assigned readings before each session develop and submit a lesson plan and a reflection plan and participate in group discussions lesson plan and reflection implementation plan assignments are designed to help participants absorb the new information and to think about how to apply it to their own classrooms while the information is still fresh in their minds stanford university all rights reserved 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints rss+ rss xml feeds
